=======
cameras
=======

Put widgets in your desktop with a webcam

============
Requirements
============

Required dependencies:

    gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
    gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0,
    gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1,
    gir1.2-notify-0.7,
    gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0,
    gir1.2-gst-plugins-base-1.0

========
Download
========

Download the package:

    $ git clone https://github.com/atareao/cameras

=======
Install
=======

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:atareao/cameras
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install cameras
